      "message": "Patch Set 9:\n\nTests received by maloo, run on CentOS release 5.8/x86_64, CentOS release 6.2/x86_64: (https://maloo.whamcloud.com/test_sessions/b15c6ec0-da5a-11e1-8f49-52540035b04c).  Ran 12 tests.  2 tests failed: sanityn, sanity.",
